    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1888-11-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1888-11-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="318"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d318">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">de Claparède</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Switzerland</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1888-11-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 27, 1888</date>. (Received November
                        27.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary</hi>: In pursuance of instructions received
                    from my Government, I have the honor to inform you that Mr. Hertenstein,
                    President of the Swiss Confederation, last night succumbed to the effects of the
                    operation performed on Saturday last.</p>
                <p>Begging you, Mr. Secretary, to communicate the intelligence of this sad and
                    painful event to the President of the United States of America,</p>
                <p>I avail, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">A. de Claparède.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
